{"tid":519131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男深宵提款　遭持刀賊劫40萬","createTime":"2018-01-04T05:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T05:33:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe9afab9e5a9d2d6cee73b538e967aa59393faf","tid":519131,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180104/s00001/73e6a6e2b3e4127ab77380551517bd1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F73e6a6e2b3e4127ab77380551517bd1e.jpg&h=82a5f714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名年約40歲內地男子報警，稱於油麻地彌敦道380號一酒店附近被劫去約40萬現金。<br />\n<br />\n男子稱，凌晨4時許，他與友人到南京街一銀行櫃員機提款，其間友人不適自行離開，男子提款後將現金放於一個隨身袋，沿馬路返回酒店，惟走至彌敦道與加士居道交界燈位過馬路時，突然有5至6名持刀賊人攔途搶劫，搶去其放有約40萬現金的隨身袋，並劫走其手機。男子在糾纏間鼻及手部受傷，他自行返回酒店向職員求助及要求代為報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，派員於現場附近一帶兜截，但沒有發現。遇劫男子在友人陪同下，於現場協助警員調查，案件列作「搶劫」跟進，警方正追輯賊人下落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180104/s00001/1515029840014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F1515029840014&d=zqmUZlESaYiEDOAqy4fqzi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d1356c08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180104%2Fs00001%2F1515029840014&h=d1235208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180104/s00001/1515029840014</a>"},{"pid":"b5ac5ff20b03a93da0e6cc23d051c57cb418823b","tid":519131,"uid":67292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"個友人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410cffc94802ce7d85b031efeadd7dc6b015c44c","tid":519131,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cac25fbcadfc329876d9d71ef3152305fdc97e